### Weapons: get
GET {{baseUrl}}/weapons/{{weaponId}}

### Weapons: create
POST {{baseUrl}}/weapons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Boltgun",
  "range": 24,
  "attacks": "2",
  "skill": "3+",
  "strength": 4,
  "armourPiercing": 1,
  "damage": 1
}

###
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/weapons/{{weaponId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "range": 35,
  "attacks": "3"
}